<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-blue);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Areas</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Guildford &amp; Surrey</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Building services across Guildford and the whole of Surrey — MEPH, commercial fit-out, fabric and external works, brought together under one accountable team. Commercial offices, business parks, healthcare estates, residential and build-to-rent all touch every trade at once, so we self-deliver the lot and hand the building over on one date. From our Burgess Hill base, Surrey is a short run up the A3 and M25.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Guildford &amp; Surrey →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">In Guildford &amp; Surrey</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One team for the<br>whole building.</h2></div><p class="body" style="max-width:62ch;margin:0 0 32px;">Surrey is a dense commercial market — the office and town-centre cores of Guildford and Woking, the business parks strung along the A3 and M25, and a mix of healthcare estates, residential and build-to-rent schemes. Much of it is occupied or live, so the work is phased and sequenced around tenants and patients rather than handed over empty. We bring MEPH, fit-out, fabric and landscaping together so services, space and envelope move as one programme.</p><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span><a href="/meph/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">MEPH</a></span></h4><ul><li>MEPH — HVAC, power, lighting &amp; public health</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span><a href="/commercial/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Commercial Fit-out</a></span></h4><ul><li>Cat A &amp; Cat B fit-out &amp; refurbishment</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span><a href="/fabric/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Fabric</a></span></h4><ul><li>Cladding, roofing, render &amp; envelope</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Landscaping</a></span></h4><ul><li>Hard &amp; soft landscaping, surfacing, boundaries</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Areas we cover</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Guildford &amp; Surrey &amp; the<br>surrounding area.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><span class="sector">Guildford</span><span class="sector">Woking</span><span class="sector">Godalming</span><span class="sector">Farnham</span><span class="sector">Camberley</span><span class="sector">Leatherhead</span><span class="sector">Epsom</span><span class="sector">Dorking</span><span class="sector">Redhill</span><span class="sector">Reigate</span><span class="sector">Cobham</span><span class="sector">Esher</span><span class="sector">Staines</span><span class="sector">Weybridge</span></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Why AMPM</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Local, accountable,<br>one team.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>On your doorstep</span></h4><ul><li><strong>South-East coverage from one base</strong> — Surrey sits a short run up the A3 and M25 from our Burgess Hill office, so the same team that covers Sussex and London delivers across the county.</li><li><strong>Business-park &amp; corporate-office experience</strong> — Cat-A landlord works through to fully-fitted Cat-B workplaces, sequenced around live buildings and fixed move-in dates.</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>One accountable team</span></h4><ul><li><strong>Healthcare &amp; residential/BTR fit</strong> — phased, occupied works on healthcare estates and the standards-led delivery that residential and build-to-rent schemes need.</li><li><strong>One team for services, fabric &amp; external works</strong> — MEPH, fit-out, fabric and landscaping self-delivered under one accountable contractor, backed by AMPM Group's accreditations.</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Guildford &amp; Surrey questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover Guildford and the rest of Surrey?</summary><p>Yes. We work right across Surrey — Guildford, Woking, Godalming, Farnham, Camberley, Leatherhead, Epsom, Dorking, Redhill, Reigate, Cobham, Esher, Staines and Weybridge among them. The county is a short run from our Burgess Hill base via the A3 and M25, so a named contact can be on site quickly.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you work on business parks and corporate offices in Surrey?</summary><p>Yes — that is core work for us. From Cat-A landlord works to a fully-fitted Cat-B workplace, an office or business-park unit touches MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works at once. We self-deliver all of it under one programme, sequenced around occupied buildings and a fixed move-in date.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover healthcare and residential/BTR schemes in Surrey?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver across healthcare estates and residential and build-to-rent schemes in Surrey, with works phased around occupied buildings — out-of-hours isolations, temporary services and floor-by-floor handover — and delivered to the relevant UK standards, backed by AMPM Group's accreditations.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Our service lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Groundworks</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green);